        <content type="html" xml:base="https://yzzfo.github.io/en/unity/other/stylized-medieval-fantasy-weapons-pack/">&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Stylized Medieval Fantasy Weapons Pack&lt;&#x2F;b&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Stylized Medieval Fantasy Weapons Pack&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; contains 20 professional weapon models. The Fantasy Weapons pack includes high-quality hand-drawn weapon textures. All weapons are mobile-friendly and 100% ready-to-play in prefabs, ready for use in your game!&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Features:&lt;&#x2F;b&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;20 Professional 3D Models&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Texture size: 2048x2048px&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;This bundle comes with an extended commercial license, which means you can use these effects to create stunning designs for yourself and your clients!&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
